# Didactic Resources
:resource_book_oa a guide:DidacticResource ;
    guide:bibliographyTitle "Design with operational amplifiers and analog integrated circuits (fourth edition)" ;
    guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" ;
    guide:bibliographyDescription "Es el principal libro de texto, de entre los recomendados, para seguir la asignatura" .

